::Hevngjerrig::
       Hevn follows Blackstorm to the mess hall and sits down across from 
her.  He leans forward with his elbows on the table and his hands folded 
together in front of him.  "So..."  He let's his brief comment go at that and 
waits for her to speak first.

--part1_1e7.808da90.2be3494d_boundary
